{
  "stem": "18470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now if I had to be searched and they found that, I wouldn't be talking to you either, so the absurdity of the risks that you take.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the other hand, my grandfather said, when they get to America, you know, you've got to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So here at least is the gold dollar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have the gold dollar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I look at it regularly to compel myself to remember these fragilities of life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it took-- it took a better part of a day to go through all of the-- the various processes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we call them today, security checks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There they wanted to make sure that you were leaving penuriously, and that you had your ticket and your-- your entrance visa.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that point, they didn't want Jews to get back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I received a special visa, because the quotas had been used up for children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Roosevelt had a special children's quota, on top of what was then permitted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I believe I came in under a special visa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my mother's visa came in the beginning of April, and mine came in May.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, it was a way of harassing, till the very end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a couple of days out, I remember there was another little boy on board whom I subsequently met as a young man.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And both of us were seasick for the seven days it took to get from Hamburg to New York.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- for some reason, either the water was very rough, but I remember being in my bunk all the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother seemed to be immune to it, because she was on deck most of the time, bringing me apples.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
